Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.02,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Kijomori\NMACUJAMA Ken'iči
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.82,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Minamoto no Jošitomo\NTAMAKI Hiroši
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.49,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Princ Masahito\NMACUDA Šota
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.40,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Sato Norikijo\NFUDŽIKI Naohito
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.24,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Usagimaru\N KATO Kodži
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.94,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Minamoto no Joritomo/vypravěč\NOKADA Masaki
